
# Tracker comment — github (https://github.com/getwyrd/wyrd)

> Voice/format for Wyrd PDCA. Issue IDs look like `#123`.
> One comment per disposition; cite the fix/PR and the evidence.

**Issue:** <id>
**Disposition:** Fixed | Already-fixed | Can't-repro | Wontfix | By-design | External | Duplicate

<one or two sentences: what was found, and the outcome>

**Evidence:**
- <repro result / log / screenshot, or pointer to the PR + commit>

**Verified against:**
- <path>:<lines> — <what was checked there, on the target branch>
